---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import heatmapImg from '../../data/B3/Heatmap.png'
import heatmapMethodImg from '../../data/B3/HeatMapMethod.png'
---

<section class="b3h-section w-[80%] mx-auto border-l border-r border-white/20">
  <div class="b3h-inner">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="b3h-header">
      <span class="b3h-badge">BLOCK 03 · TERRITORIAL DENSITY</span>
      <h2 class="b3h-title">Mining Sites Density Map</h2>
      <p class="b3h-subtitle">
        Spatial distribution of mining sites with a known extraction method. The density
        maps confirm that mining activity is concentrated along the
        <strong>Andes mountain range</strong>, with the main hotspots in the
        <strong>central Andes</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Heatmap general -->
    <figure class="b3h-figure">
      <div class="b3h-img-wrapper">
        <Image
          src={heatmapImg}
          alt="Density map of mining sites with known method in Peru"
          widths={[600, 900, 1200]}
          sizes="(max-width: 768px) 90vw, 1040px"
          class="b3h-img"
        />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="b3h-caption">Density of mining sites with known method</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <!-- Heatmap por método -->
    <figure class="b3h-figure">
      <div class="b3h-img-wrapper">
        <Image
          src={heatmapMethodImg}
          alt="Density map of mining sites by extraction method in Peru"
          widths={[600, 900, 1200]}
          sizes="(max-width: 768px) 90vw, 1040px"
          class="b3h-img"
        />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="b3h-caption">Site density by extraction method</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <!-- Contextual insight -->
    <div class="b3h-insight">
      <span class="b3h-insight__icon">🔍</span>
      <p class="b3h-insight__text">
        <strong>Identified territorial clusters:</strong> The
        <strong>central Andes</strong> (Junín, Pasco, Lima, Ancash, Huancavelica) concentrate underground
        mining associated with the Zn-Pb-Ag polymetallic vein strip. The
        <strong>southern Andes</strong> (Arequipa, Cusco, Apurímac, Tacna, Moquegua) show greater
        open-pit operations, linked to large porphyry Cu deposits. In the
        <strong>north</strong> (Cajamarca, La Libertad), underground extraction predominates for
        vein-type gold deposits. The distribution of methods follows the geology of Peru's metallogenic belts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .b3h-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .b3h-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  /* Header */
  .b3h-header {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .b3h-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.15);
  }

  .b3h-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .b3h-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .b3h-subtitle strong {
    color: var(--accent-lime-light);
  }

  /* Figures */
  .b3h-figure {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .b3h-img-wrapper {
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .b3h-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .b3h-caption {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  /* Insight */
  .b3h-insight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.12);
  }

  .b3h-insight__icon {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .b3h-insight__text {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .b3h-insight__text strong {
    color: var(--accent-lime-light);
  }
</style>
